              "fill": "$--text",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Hey team,\n\nAttached are the latest Figma exports for the new dashboard layout. I've incorporated the feedback from yesterday's sync, specifically focusing on:\n\n• Tightening the padding around the main data grid component\n• Updating the primary action buttons to use the new core black color token\n• Simplifying the filter dropdowns into a unified modal\n\nLet me know what you think. If we're good with this direction, I'll start prepping the redlines for engineering handoff on Thursday.\n\nBest,\nSarah",
